(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Cell.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind organelles and how cell parts) Tj
T*
(work together.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct process explanation step by step instead of jumping to the answer.) Tj
T*
